{"tid":1318500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民陣發表聲明","createTime":"2019-07-15T03:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T10:37:05.000Z","uid":212626,"like":88,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a2276e3523331793242b2a4aa3ea57275dec5c22","tid":1318500,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:00:14.000Z","msg":"民陣就周六日的大規模警民衝突表達強烈擔憂<br />\n<br />\n民陣作出以下聲明︰<br />\n<br />\n就周六日在各區遊行的相關情況，造成我們不願意見到的傷害，我們認為，始作俑者始終是深潛多日的林鄭月娥。如果政府是有心保護前線警員，以及不願再見到市民在抗議行動中受傷，政府應更積極地回應市民在反送中運動的訴求。<br />\n<br />\n民間要求的獨立調查委員會，是有理有據，對於林鄭月娥政府而言，已是回應市民訴求，平息民怨的最有效方法，林鄭必須如她在7月9日的記者會所講，了解局勢，對民怨有準確的掌握，回應訴求，設立獨立調查委員會，否則這場運動終將會因為持續的警民衝突，造成無可挽回的人命傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線<br />\n2019年7月15日<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/photos/a.517931904920872/2356470161067028/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCivilHumanRightsFront%2Fphotos%2Fa.517931904920872%2F2356470161067028%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=MD3su0BfWHBnm8Iidd6ZKSq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=45f89689\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/photos/a.517931904920872/2356470161067028/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"6f6c2f08ab09c36acacf9f8d12f7c8013328deff","tid":1318500,"uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:00:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yBCOYPN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyBCOYPN.jpg&h=c55f683f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b455b5a8e18504359c6233c625e034f5152eb01","tid":1318500,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:02:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ec6cd608a1aaec2e3d823fa6f60a8e98d286b7","tid"