ort.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n學藍絲話齋，如果係外國，個警察死撚左喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1316434\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1316434</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6510b152f529966cac423e3c6df1cea7bf80526d","tid":1318500,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:08:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278c970d1fa2bb08020b32ad8d5133f23a30b043","tid":1318500,"uid":25168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:13:02.000Z","msg":"［一定要去］今晚金鍾要人呀！！！！！！我地需要陳伯！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1318400\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1318400</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qoPUREZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqoPUREZ.png&h=ae5035c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oc2GwEZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foc2GwEZ.png&h=0244a2d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04cfb71aeb3bac012f7699e8c0fb9950ffd5c83a","tid":1318500,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:29:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8b86d9738353d972a0e414fbb2a9514b8d0029e","tid":1318500,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:39:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1236dce0088ee819de8fed9a3cae7349b3ea526c","tid":1318500,"uid":237355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:22:19.000Z","msg":"pu'sh"},{"pid":"e57b933e88c4b2e0dafaea86c2b51e43091cdee3","tid":1318500,"uid":126099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:26:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c38c6196c5f5dc73940a454e55acf6029862d13","tid":1318500,"uid":212626,"like":0,"di